<br />
<br />I've seen a number of specialised programs, but a lot of them are for PC, and they all seem quite tricky for a noob like me to use.
<br />
<br />Again, i have a lot of questions relating to graphics, but firstly i guess i just need to know, am i currently in a position to get going?
<br />
<br />Thanks again, and sorry for being a complete noob <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /></div>

