					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Animations is one of the things that Photoshop isn't too good at. GraphicsGale has animation support (you can switch between frames with a hotkey, and also see animation preview at the same time), and able to export animation frames as a sheet, which is very handy for conversion.</div>

					
